data.description: Move-in Ready Rancher Full Of New!  New Vivant Home Security Sysem.  New stand up shower!  New durable beautiful smartcore premium vinyl flooring that are water proof, scatch proof, anti allergen, true to life, that reduce sound. New 2021 Samsung smart Washing Mashine.  New Exterior And Interior Paint! Child safe and child proof Throughout the whole house!  New roof! 6-panel Doors! Large Open Kitchen W/ Nice Cabinets,Stainless Steel Appliances And Tile Floors! Updated Vinyl Windows W/ Faux Wood Blinds. Spacious Dining Area And Roomy Living Room. Washer And Dryer Stay! Don't Miss The Oversized Garage!! Fantastic Park Just A Few Blocks Away!  Amazing view of the mountains from backyard patio!  Close To 3 Parks, Widefield Neighborehood Community Library, Widefield Neighborhood Sports fields,  Widefield Neighborhood Pool, 5 Neighborhood Open Spaces, Schools, Churches, And Ft. Carson! This Is A Must See!
